\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 For I know mine iniquity, and my sin is ever before me. Against Thee only have I sinned and done this evil before Thee, that Thou mightest be justified in Thy words, and prevail when Thou \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 
