\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4355983\charrsid4355983 \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, deprive me not of Thy heavenly good things. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, d\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 eliver me from the eternal torments.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, if I have sinned in mind or thought, in word or deed, forgive me. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, deliver me from all ignorance, forgetfulness, faint-heartedness, and stony insensibility. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, deliver me from every temptation. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, enlighten my heart which evil desire hath darkened. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, as a man I have sinned, but do Thou, as the compassionate God, have mercy on me, seeing the infirmity of my soul. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, send Thy grace to my \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 help, that I may glorify Thy holy name. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord Jesus Christ, write me Thy servant in the Book of Life, and grant me a good end. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord my God, even though I have done nothing good in Thy sight, yet grant me by Thy grace to make a good beginning. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord,\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37  sprinkle into my heart the dew of Thy grace. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord of heaven and earth, remember me Thy sinful servant, shameful and unclean, in Thy kingdom. Amen.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, accept me in penitence. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, forsake me not. O Lord, lead me not into temptation. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, gr\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 ant me good thoughts. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, grant me tears, and remembrance of death, and compunction. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, grant me the thought of confessing my sins. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, grant me humility, chastity, and obedience.
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, grant me patience, courage, and meekness. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, i\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 mplant in me the root of good, Thy fear in my heart. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, vouchsafe me to love Thee with all my soul and thoughts, and in all things to do Thy will. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lord, protect me from evil men, and demons, and passions, and from every other unseemly thing. 
\par \hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 O Lo\hich\af37\dbch\af37\loch\f37 rd, Thou knowest that Thou doest as Thou wilt: Thy will be done also in me a sinner; for blessed art Thou unto the ages. Amen.
